content: I'm trying to help answer questions here. When I am on a question, I go look for an answer and then can't get back to the question to answer it unless I remember exactly where I was. I've used Discord before somewhere else but having difficulty finding my way around here.
Hello <@911700060360818688> we appreciate you are eager to support other volunteers. You can go back with ctrl (or cmd)+], but you don't need to answer the questions, our staff will take care of it.
